com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange
Class DataResult

java.lang.Object
  com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.DataResult

public class DataResult
extends Object

This class stores data results and includes the number of created, deleted, updated or invalid records. It also contains table schema node, error and warning messages.
